## Legal Notice

This application is a proxy service that provides access to the Pédantix game 
(https://pedantix.certitudes.org/). All game content, logic, and intellectual 
property belong to the original creators at certitudes.org. This proxy does 
not modify, store, or redistribute game content - it simply provides network 
access when the original site is blocked by network restrictions.

The proxy service is provided for educational and accessibility purposes only.